The paper deals with a wireless communication system with energy harvesting and multiple antennas, which falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a novel protocol for relaying, which involves decision-making and optimization, making it relevant to systems and control (cs.SY). The use of multiple antennas and relaying also falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and game theory (cs.GT).
